      public static double getScore(Piece piece, double score, double weight)
      Computes the score (contribution) of a piece based on its type and weight.
      Parameters:
      piece - The type of piece (SINGLE, DOUBLE, or MIXED).
      score - The current score to be updated.
      weight - The weight multiplier for the piece type.
      Returns:

    • getScoreWrapper

      public static double getScoreWrapper(MoveGenerator moveGenerator, Color player, double depth)
      Computes the score of the current game position for a specified player.
      Parameters:
      moveGenerator - The MoveGenerator object providing game state information.
      player - The color of the player for whom the score is computed (BLUE or RED).

      Returns:

      Parameters:
      moveGenerator - The MoveGenerator object providing game state information.
      player - The color of the player for whom the score is computed (BLUE or RED).
      depth - The current depth of evaluation in the search tree.
      moves - The opponent's moves represented as a map of combined integer start and end positions.
      Returns:
      The computed score for the player in the current position.
